A driver crashed his expensive Ferrari on Sunday in Sandton, Joburg. Pictures of the expensive ride are doing rounds on social media. It it said that the car crashed a raided circle outside Houghton Golf club. The driver unhurt but shaken. People on Social Media felt sorry for the driver who will have to pay a lot of money to repair his car. Some even joked that if his insurance company sees these pictures, they will spend the whole night moving their offices... and tomorrow they will be nowhere to be found. 